  "subject": "Refactored run() in AuditThread",
  "commit_message": "Refactored run() in AuditThread\n\nSonar was complaining about a nested try/catch block in the\nrun method of AuditThread. It recommended moving the logic\ncontained within the inner try/catch to a separate method.\n\nThe nested try/catch block is necessary to capture the\nexceptions properly, and have the thread continue to run.\nHowever, separating the code as recommended by sonar\nresults in more readable code.\n\n[POLICY-96]\n\nChange-Id: I7a4eeebceeb3557841ed668c300b92d36b384292\nSigned-off-by: Magnusen, Drew (dm741q) <dm741q@att.com>\n",
